Class EfsDispatchersConfig

java.lang.Object
org.efs.dispatcher.config.EfsDispatchersConfig
public final class EfsDispatchersConfig extends Object
Contains list of EfsDispatcherConfig instances. This class is defined as a typesafe configuration bean.

Example EfsDispatchersConfig File Entry

dispatchers : [
  {
    dispatcherName = AlgoDispatcher
    threadType = SPINNING
    numThreads = 1
    priority = 10
    eventQueueCapacity = 128
    maxEvents = 128
    runQueueCapacity = 8
  },
  {
    dispatcherName = MonitorDispatcher
    threadType = SPINPARK
    numThreads = 1
    priority = 8
    spinLimit = 1000000
    parkTime = 500 nanos
    eventQueueCapacity = 256
    maxEvents = 64
    runQueueCapacity = 16
  },
  {
    dispatcherName = UtilityDispatcher
    threadType = BLOCKING
    numThreads = 4
    priority = 1
    eventQueueCapacity = 0 // Unlimited event queue size.
    maxEvents = 8
    runQueueCapacity = 64
  }
]
